Problem Statement

Colaberry school of Data Analytics has a great program. This program is unique and different from the normal process, The  Graduate can apply for a job that was selected for them based of certain criteria to make the submission valuable. It was implemented to test if Colaberry could use the data to give their upcoming  Grads a competitive edge when interviewing in this market. The plan would decide it the Program would move forward or dissolve.

To get more information about Colaberry school of Data Analytics http://www.colaberry.com/
